name: Finny Fish: Fight For Freedom ( Level 2)
name_original: Finny Fish: Fight For Freedom ( Level 2)
description: Welcome! This is the 2nd level to Finny Fish: Fight For Freedom! In this level the player controls Finny the Fish and must guide him  out of the pipes while avoiding floating pieces of trash. The game controls with either the WASD keys or arrow keys. Can you help Finny exit the pipes and make his way to the ocean?
